Dialogue: 0,0:01:11.59,0:01:16.03,Default,,0,0,0,,第2次 学园偶像季 决定举办！
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.73,0:01:20.71,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是樱坂导演
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.01,0:01:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,你喜欢就好
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.58,0:01:27.23,Default,,0,0,0,,负责剪辑的小璃奈和小侑也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:28.39,0:01:29.33,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.76,0:01:31.32,Default,,0,0,0,,大家也辛苦了
Dialogue: 0,0:01:31.53,0:01:34.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真想让粉丝们也快点看到
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.44,0:01:36.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这个 会马上传到网上吗
Dialogue: 0,0:01:36.90,0:01:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,现在正在和学生会商量宣传场地
Dialogue: 0,0:01:41.70,0:01:44.84,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然学生会长本人就在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:01:46.16,0:01:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这次 我希望能让更多的学园偶像和粉丝参与进来
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.37,0:01:55.68,Default,,0,0,0,,上次那么热闹 这次一定也会来很多人的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:55.68,0:01:59.18,Default,,0,0,0,,而且上传的视频也有这么多的点击量
Dialogue: 0,0:01:59.18,0:02:04.22,Default,,0,0,0,,除了东云和藤黄 还有许多高中也联系了我们
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.38,0:02:07.21,Default,,0,0,0,,总觉得好开心呢
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.11,0:02:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,为了回应大家的期待 今天也要全力以赴好好练习
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.92,0:02:16.86,Default,,0,0,0,,但在那之前
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.17,0:02:22.04,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞霞准备了特制可焙面包 先把肚子填饱吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.70,0:02:25.09,Default,,0,0,0,,放开吃吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.76,0:02:43.22,STAFF,,0,0,20,,{\an2\fs40\b1\bord2.5}钟岚珠：我来日本了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.72,0:02:57.54,Default,,0,0,0,,学园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.99,0:03:02.63,Default,,0,0,0,,歌我听过了 还不错
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.38,0:03:04.52,Default,,0,0,0,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.09,0:03:06.93,Default,,0,0,0,,那可是我写的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.12,0:03:10.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好了 出发吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.06,0:03:26.65,TITLE,,0,0,0,,{\blur3\fad(300,0)\pos(1108.19,614.704)}第1集 新的悸动
Dialogue: 0,0:03:36.84,0:03:38.20,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.20,0:03:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.48,0:03:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,又熬夜练琴了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.64,0:03:45.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.19,0:03:48.15,Default,,0,0,0,,已经习惯音乐科了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.84,0:03:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟才刚转过去不久
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.42,0:03:54.46,Default,,0,0,0,,现在不仅要补上学期的课程
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.46,0:03:57.06,Default,,0,0,0,,每天还要坚持练琴
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.52,0:03:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不要太勉强自己
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.14,0:04:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,没事没事
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.75,0:04:04.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这都是我想做的 没事的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.14,0:04:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,加油 小霞霞
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.82,0:04:15.83,Default,,0,0,0,,我们能不能上台 全看你了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.83,0:04:18.59,Default,,0,0,0,,别给我压力啊
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.59,0:04:23.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好嘞 那就让爱姐我们把好运分给你
Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.50,0:04:26.04,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 嗯 仅止于运
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.04,0:04:28.69,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的 请你们认真一点
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.69,0:04:29.88,Default,,0,0,0,,但是我好像…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.22,0:04:31.70,Default,,0,0,0,,有了一种…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.16,0:04:34.49,Default,,0,0,0,,会成功的感觉
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.25,0:04:39.89,Default,,0,0,0,,下半学期 有相当多的校内活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.89,0:04:43.63,Default,,0,0,0,,最先到来的虹咲学园开放日
Dialogue: 0,0:04:43.63,0:04:48.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是每年由全校学生一起为想要就读虹咲的初中生们
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.48,0:04:51.36,Default,,0,0,0,,准备各种体验课程和社团介绍的活动
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.02,0:04:57.68,Default,,0,0,0,,只有大家齐心协力 我们才能把活动办好
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.44,0:05:00.69,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们一起把活动办好吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.81,0:05:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.27,0:05:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,今年大家对学园偶像的关注度更高了
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.68,0:05:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,应该会非常热闹
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.71,0:05:10.62,Default,,0,0,0,,是 是有这个可能
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.31,0:05:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我是普通科1年级的三船栞子
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.17,0:05:15.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以问一个问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.89,0:05:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,可以
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.23,0:05:18.57,Default,,0,0,0,,请问在社团说明会上
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.57,0:05:22.65,Default,,0,0,0,,学园偶像同好会发表的具体内容是什么呢
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.17,0:05:27.57,Default,,0,0,0,,听说是关于下一次学园偶像季的相关通知
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.96,0:05:30.53,Default,,0,0,0,,关于这个 我也事先调查了一下
Dialogue: 0,0:05:31.25,0:05:33.32,Default,,0,0,0,,“能够实现大家梦想的地方”
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.82,0:05:35.81,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为这是个非常棒的理念
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,如果这个活动能为我们带来积极的影响
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.24,0:05:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,我也想尽自己的一份力
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.21,0:05:45.03,Default,,0,0,0,,届时请多多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.94,0:05:47.46,Default,,0,0,0,,学生会长？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.72,0:05:53.00,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 当天不能办演唱会啊
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.00,0:05:54.43,Default,,0,0,0,,惭愧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.43,0:05:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,好不甘心
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.65,0:05:58.34,Default,,0,0,0,,这也没办法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.34,0:06:02.91,Default,,0,0,0,,我们学校有这么多社团 要抽中一定很难吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.91,0:06:05.95,Default,,0,0,0,,就算没有抽中 我们也能用西栋的活动大楼
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.27,0:06:08.60,Default,,0,0,0,,当天我们就在那里发传单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.60,0:06:11.12,Default,,0,0,0,,除此之外 我们还有别的事要做
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.41,0:06:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,其实刚刚通过讨论
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.65,0:06:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,我们可以用东栋的大屏幕来播放宣传视频
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.90,0:06:21.74,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然能用的时间有限 但宣传效果一定非常棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.17,0:06:23.93,Default,,0,0,0,,好棒
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.57,0:06:27.12,Default,,0,0,0,,你们两个 怎么啦
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.33,0:06:28.44,Default,,0,0,0,,侑前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.48,0:06:32.45,Default,,0,0,0,,如果还有一周的时间 应该还可以把视频做得更好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.21,0:06:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,难得有机会让大家看 我们希望能做到最好
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.21,0:06:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,也是 我明白了 就这么办吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.21,0:06:46.45,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也不能输 一起为学园开放日加油吧
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.45,0:06:47.26,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.50,0:06:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,一起加油
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.73,0:07:11.13,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.55,0:07:12.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还在尝试
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.92,0:07:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,每次改了一个地方 就又想改另一个地方了
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.71,0:07:17.88,Default,,0,0,0,,也是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.85,0:07:20.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没完没了了啊
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.21,0:07:22.69,Default,,0,0,0,,这些文件夹是干什么用的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.69,0:07:25.56,Default,,0,0,0,,是用来放用不上的视频素材的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.41,0:07:27.67,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以看看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.99,0:07:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,等我们先做完再说吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.55,0:07:44.41,Default,,0,0,0,,参加学园开放日的各位请从这边进入
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.15,0:07:47.08,Default,,0,0,0,,请
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.70,0:07:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.73,0:07:51.00,Default,,0,0,0,,祝你们玩得开心
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.00,0:07:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.79,0:07:53.40,Default,,0,0,0,,有我的份吗
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.67,0:07:56.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了 栞子
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.51,0:07:59.95,Default,,0,0,0,,好久不见 岚珠
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.78,0:08:02.87,Default,,0,0,0,,我想见几个人
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.06,0:08:06.19,Default,,0,0,0,,能带我去学园偶像同好会吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.43,0:08:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,学园偶像…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.33,0:08:13.91,Default,,0,0,0,,今年也来了好多人啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.30,0:08:19.49,Default,,0,0,0,,早知道这样 我们初中的时候也来看看就好了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.78,0:08:24.08,Default,,0,0,0,,因为家里比较近 所以没怎么考虑就选了这里呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:24.08,0:08:26.44,Default,,0,0,0,,不过结果好就行
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.93,0:08:30.25,Default,,0,0,0,,现在我也找到了自己想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.89,0:08:31.97,Default,,0,0,0,,是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.92,0:08:34.70,Default,,0,0,0,,小侑 接下来怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.70,0:08:36.85,Default,,0,0,0,,我要回去剪视频
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.15,0:08:38.54,Default,,0,0,0,,还没剪完吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.54,0:08:41.11,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 只剩一点点了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.51,0:08:46.09,Default,,0,0,0,,音乐科那边也很忙吧 你真的忙得过来吗
Dialogue: 0,0:08:46.09,0:08:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 不过前阵子的小测试挂科就是了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.96,0:08:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,没事 你就放心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.56,0:08:55.67,Default,,0,0,0,,可是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.67,0:08:56.94,Default,,0,0,0,,找到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,不要在走廊奔跑
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.85,0:09:01.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你就是步梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.55,0:09:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,终于见到你了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.79,0:09:17.09,Default,,0,0,0,,我是为了成为学园偶像 从香港来到虹咲的短期留学生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.11,0:09:19.19,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.58,0:09:23.04,Default,,0,0,0,,留学生？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.46,0:09:27.10,Default,,0,0,0,,为了当学园偶像 千里迢迢从香港过来？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.10,0:09:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,和我一样
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.39,0:09:32.66,Default,,0,0,0,,初次见面 我叫钟岚珠
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.66,0:09:35.89,Default,,0,0,0,,我听说除了你以外 还有一个留学生
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.89,0:09:39.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她对学园偶像没什么兴趣
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.85,0:09:44.07,STAFF,,0,0,0,,{\fs33\b1}流水素面同好会
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.38,0:09:42.72,Default,,0,0,0,,现在应该在学校的什么地方吧
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.44,0:09:45.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这样啊
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.03,0:09:49.66,Default,,0,0,0,,那我就先回自己的岗位了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:49.89,0:09:52.04,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢 帮大忙了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.04,0:09:54.58,Default,,0,0,0,,从小一起长大就是好
Dialogue: 0,0:09:54.58,0:09:56.87,Default,,0,0,0,,同好会的各位 我就先告辞了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.38,0:09:59.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我在东栋等你们
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.97,0:10:03.00,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.00,0:10:07.79,Default,,0,0,0,,但如果是为了学园偶像 其他也有不少有名的学校吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.79,0:10:09.55,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么要来虹咲呢
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.74,0:10:12.99,Default,,0,0,0,,因为我看了学园偶像季的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.38,0:10:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,我被深深地打动了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.83,0:10:23.13,Default,,0,0,0,,每个人都表现着自己想做的事
Dialogue: 0,0:10:23.13,0:10:24.60,Default,,0,0,0,,闪闪发光着
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.89,0:10:27.84,Default,,0,0,0,,让我也对那个舞台产生了向往
Dialogue: 0,0:10:28.21,0:10:30.68,Default,,0,0,0,,一想到过了高中就再也没有机会了
Dialogue: 0,0:10:30.96,0:10:33.55,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我就来到了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.17,0:10:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,我好高兴
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.10,0:10:41.55,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎来到虹咲学园学园偶像同好会
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.55,0:10:45.09,Default,,0,0,0,,稍后我们会播放下次偶像季的宣传视频
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.09,0:10:46.15,Default,,0,0,0,,要一起看吗
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.15,0:10:48.76,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗 要看要看
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.76,0:10:53.26,Default,,0,0,0,,为了让更多的人看到 要加油发传单啦
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.26,0:10:57.00,Default,,0,0,0,,雪雪还有运营的工作 不能过来对吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.00,0:11:00.05,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 小雫和小璃奈呢
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.05,0:11:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,听说还在剪辑
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.33,0:11:05.41,Default,,0,0,0,,我也得过去找她们了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:05.75,0:11:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,不行
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.70,0:11:11.67,Default,,0,0,0,,让你三个在一起肯定又要改个没完没了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:12.04,0:11:13.75,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.75,0:11:16.25,Default,,0,0,0,,这件事就交给我
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.25,0:11:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,让我们在大屏幕前见吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.98,0:11:22.77,Default,,0,0,0,,那就交给小霞 我们去发传单吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.45,0:11:27.01,Default,,0,0,0,,我们是学园偶像同好会
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.01,0:11:28.95,Default,,0,0,0,,请多关照
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.95,0:11:30.27,Default,,0,0,0,,我认识你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.27,0:11:31.47,Default,,0,0,0,,我看过你的视频
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.47,0:11:34.21,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗 谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.21,0:11:37.81,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我们又要办演唱会了 有机会要来看看哦
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.81,0:11:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好
Dialogue: 0,0:11:38.69,0:11:42.15,Default,,0,0,0,,请问 你是上原步梦吧
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.15,0:11:44.94,Default,,0,0,0,,可以跟我一起拍张照吗
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.12,0:11:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,当然可以
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.22,0:11:49.83,Default,,0,0,0,,来 茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.83,0:11:51.09,Default,,0,0,0,,茄子
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.07,0:11:53.41,Default,,0,0,0,,下次见
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.62,0:11:56.84,Default,,0,0,0,,差不多快开播了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:12:01.15,Default,,0,0,0,,侑侑和步梦先带岚珠去东栋吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.15,0:12:04.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我们等发完传单了再过去
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.93,0:12:06.32,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯 好
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.89,0:12:07.97,Default,,0,0,0,,我们走吧
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.56,0:12:14.62,Default,,0,0,0,,我想把学园偶像季办成 只要有爱
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.62,0:12:17.60,Default,,0,0,0,,人人都能参与其中的节日
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.94,0:12:21.86,Default,,0,0,0,,能自由地参与任何社团 不加入社团也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.26,0:12:24.53,Default,,0,0,0,,就算不是虹咲的学生也没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.98,0:12:28.71,Default,,0,0,0,,只要能和大家互相分享自己心中的喜欢就行了
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.62,0:12:32.42,Default,,0,0,0,,听着还真有趣
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.84,0:12:36.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不过我有些在意
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.16,0:12:39.47,Default,,0,0,0,,你是新人偶像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:12:39.47,0:12:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,我好像没在视频里看到过你
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.40,0:12:44.88,Default,,0,0,0,,我不是学园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.01,0:12:50.47,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么你不是学园偶像 却在同好会里
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.29,0:12:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,因为学园偶像给了我梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.99,0:13:01.87,Default,,0,0,0,,所以现在 我想为大家的梦想加油 这就是我在同好会的理由
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.82,0:13:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也是因为有同好会的大家 小侑 还有粉丝们的支持
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.54,0:13:11.72,Default,,0,0,0,,才能在学园偶像这条路上走下去
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.44,0:13:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,粉丝支持偶像吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.78,0:13:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,已经没时间啦  动作快点
Dialogue: 0,0:13:24.06,0:13:24.80,Default,,0,0,0,,好了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.50,0:13:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,东西我带走了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:27.82,0:13:29.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好 赶紧出发
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.39,0:13:35.49,Default,,0,0,0,,马上就要开始了 来得及吗
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.08,0:13:35.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs40}…前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.77,0:13:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.11,0:13:39.83,Default,,0,0,0,,前辈 这个给你
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.83,0:13:41.17,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦你了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.49,0:13:49.67,Default,,0,0,0,,再不快点 学园偶像同好会的视频就要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.13,0:13:58.49,Default,,0,0,0,,终于要开始了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.62,0:14:00.75,Default,,0,0,0,,要放了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.78,0:14:11.59,Default,,0,0,0,,这这这这这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.59,0:14:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,是那些用不上的视频素材…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.09,0:14:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,搞错了 哇哇哇
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.23,0:14:21.23,Default,,0,0,0,,好像是弄错了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.23,0:14:24.43,Default,,0,0,0,,但这样不是也挺可爱的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.36,0:14:29.79,Default,,0,0,0,,让我再睡一会儿 艾玛
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.35,0:14:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,马上给我关掉
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.06,0:14:36.59,Default,,0,0,0,,果林前辈
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我去把对的拿过来
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.56,0:14:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.36,0:14:42.59,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞霞也去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.59,0:14:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,我也去
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,这就没了？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.89,0:14:49.73,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然不知道是什么情况 但是挺有意思的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.73,0:14:51.48,Default,,0,0,0,,再去其他地方转转吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.48,0:14:52.10,Default,,0,0,0,,嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.10,0:14:54.08,Default,,0,0,0,,是出了什么问题吗
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.08,0:14:57.01,Default,,0,0,0,,会长 到学科说明会的时间了
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.01,0:14:58.72,Default,,0,0,0,,我们去演讲厅吧
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.99,0:15:04.21,Default,,0,0,0,,好不容易聚起来的人都要走了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.52,0:15:05.94,Default,,0,0,0,,出什么问题了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:06.40,0:15:07.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你是刚才的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.81,0:15:09.95,Default,,0,0,0,,可以帮忙延后一下播放的时间吗
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.62,0:15:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,对不起 我们不能对你们特殊对待
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.82,0:15:20.74,Default,,0,0,0,,来到这里的大多数人 并不是为了学园偶像而来的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:21.54,0:15:22.85,Default,,0,0,0,,非常遗憾
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.46,0:15:24.70,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没问题啦
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.14,0:15:28.49,Default,,0,0,0,,包在我身上
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.73,0:15:38.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我要参加的学园偶像季出了问题
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.34,0:15:40.51,Default,,0,0,0,,我可不能坐视不管
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.19,0:15:44.89,Default,,0,0,0,,只要把大家吸引到这里来就行了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:44.89,0:15:45.85,Default,,0,0,0,,米娅
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.43,0:15:47.57,Default,,0,0,0,,好 好
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.96,0:15:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,借我一用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.02,0:15:56.72,Default,,0,0,0,,你要做什么
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.59,0:16:02.72,Default,,0,0,0,,大家注意
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.91,0:16:05.97,Default,,0,0,0,,就这么回去的话可就亏了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.24,0:16:10.15,Default,,0,0,0,,接下来是学园偶像 钟岚珠的出道演出
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.84,0:16:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,把这传说的开始深深烙进你的心中吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.37,0:18:14.45,Default,,0,0,0,,侑前辈 给你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.11,0:18:15.99,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,在没有边际的天空对岸
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.94,0:18:32.11,Default,,0,0,0,,岚珠 本校规定不能在演讲厅以外的场地唱歌
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.11,0:18:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,是这样的吗
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.96,0:18:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是大家都开心吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.34,0:18:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不管是出于什么理由
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.72,0:18:42.16,Default,,0,0,0,,既然你成为了虹咲的学生就要交检讨书
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.48,0:18:47.85,Default,,0,0,0,,记得在一周内交上来
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.63,0:18:51.47,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢你 小岚珠
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.47,0:18:53.24,Default,,0,0,0,,演出也非常精彩
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.24,0:18:54.55,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.55,0:18:58.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我应该也能参加学园偶像季吧
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.22,0:19:00.23,Default,,0,0,0,,那还用说
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.23,0:19:01.82,Default,,0,0,0,,大家一起参加吧
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.11,0:19:05.15,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎你来到同好会
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.49,0:19:07.16,Default,,0,0,0,,我就不加入你们了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.69,0:19:10.94,Default,,0,0,0,,我似乎和你们的想法有些不同
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.08,0:19:13.74,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？这是什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.01,0:19:16.20,Default,,0,0,0,,三船
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.20,0:19:17.18,Default,,0,0,0,,会长
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.18,0:19:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,发生什么事了吗
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.98,0:19:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,这个…
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.17,0:19:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,我想成为能迷倒所有人的学园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.47,0:19:30.46,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为偶像给粉丝梦想是一件很棒的事
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.20,0:19:33.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但是这样就足够了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.23,0:19:39.09,Default,,0,0,0,,失去了他人的支持就无法表演的偶像 太不像话了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.95,0:19:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,喂
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.91,0:19:45.63,Default,,0,0,0,,我会以个人的名义参加学园偶像季
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.86,0:19:49.61,Default,,0,0,0,,我认为在这个同好会无法实现我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.61,0:19:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,所以我要一个人干
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.45,0:19:55.39,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我再问你一次 侑
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.83,0:19:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,你为什么要待在这里
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.54,0:20:02.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我是因为被学园偶像打动
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.48,0:20:05.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为了梦想才来到这里的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.42,0:20:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,但你的梦想并不是成为学园偶像吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.80,0:20:10.65,Default,,0,0,0,,那你就应该离开同好会
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.85,0:20:13.24,Default,,0,0,0,,全力去追逐你的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:18.36,0:20:20.81,Default,,0,0,0,,你确实很了不起
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.39,0:20:25.69,Default,,0,0,0,,无论是在舞台上 还是言语中 你都很敢于去表现自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.13,0:20:26.91,Default,,0,0,0,,但是
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.25,0:20:31.65,Default,,0,0,0,,我并不认为 自己会在追逐梦想的这份心上输给你
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然现在还有很长的路要走
Dialogue: 0,0:20:35.95,0:20:42.08,Default,,0,0,0,,但我也会用我自己的方式 在这个同好会实现我的梦想
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.02,0:20:45.12,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也一样
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.42,0:20:49.65,Default,,0,0,0,,大家都是为了自己想做的事才加入了这里
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.92,0:20:56.25,Default,,0,0,0,,我会在学园偶像季上证明自己
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.89,0:21:01.72,Default,,0,0,0,,在学园偶像季上最受人瞩目的一定是我
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.34,0:21:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,正合我意
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.29,0:21:06.34,Default,,0,0,0,,有趣的事又增加了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.79,0:21:09.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就让我们用自己的表演说话吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.33,0:21:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,拜拜
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.17,0:21:18.08,Default,,0,0,0,,搞什么 那个人到底想干吗
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.08,0:21:21.53,Default,,0,0,0,,但她的表演真的很精彩呀
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.53,0:21:26.86,Default,,0,0,0,,她一定是在来日本前练习了很多
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.86,0:21:30.34,Default,,0,0,0,,我们一定要加倍努力才行
Dialogue: 0,0:21:30.34,0:21:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,小侑
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.42,0:21:36.14,Default,,0,0,0,,就算我们的梦想不一样 我也会永远支持你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.69,0:21:40.01,Default,,0,0,0,,小霞霞也会全力帮助你的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.01,0:21:41.99,Default,,0,0,0,,我们也是
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.59,0:21:47.72,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢大家
Dialogue: 0,0:23:21.02,0:23:22.20,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样了
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.21,0:23:27.42,Default,,0,0,0,,不愧是虹咲 还有这么有趣的偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.77,0:23:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,之前认识的女孩刚好也是学园偶像
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.23,0:23:34.06,Default,,0,0,0,,下次我去问问她
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.99,0:23:39.67,Default,,0,0,0,,下集 交织的色彩
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.39,0:16:20.46,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}露一手给你们看看
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.68,0:16:23.50,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}Hey～
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.28,0:16:25.43,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.74,0:16:27.10,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}准备好没？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.30,0:17:05.41,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}欢迎来到我的天地
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.22,0:17:21.22,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}我就是那么完美
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.63,0:17:40.31,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}Top of the TOP.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.31,0:17:42.20,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}Top of the WORLD.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:42.20,0:17:44.12,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}Top of the TOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.12,0:17:46.30,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}这地球就是绕着我转
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.30,0:17:47.88,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}Top of the TOP.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.88,0:17:49.73,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}Top of the WORLD.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.73,0:17:51.62,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}Top of the TOP!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.24,0:17:54.82,INYangMing,,0,0,20,,{\fs45\fsp1\blur1\fad(150,150)}怎么样 不错吧 嗯？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:31.55,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}带给你更多激情 让你光梭似箭
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:36.07,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}把你的心带向更高更远
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.45,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}压倒性的魅力
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.10,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}你定会有所共鸣 不是吗？（是我吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:58.94,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}送给你这份悸动 来吧 这里就是舞台
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.96,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}若你仅此 便乐得自胜
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:03.09,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}岂不是美中不足 所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:09.38,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}余之行路 能有何人可及
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:13.42,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}　共觞孤城之上 苍穹之景
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:17.22,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}如此饕餮 惟余独晓
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:25.84,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}让你就此流离 让你更加沉醉
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:29.60,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}将我的魅力 全部注入你的灵魂
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:33.34,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}已无一物可有畏惧 欢愉之宴业已终结
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:38.47,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}便在此时 让一切就此开始
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.24,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)\fs30}我就是万里挑一
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.59,0:16:31.55,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}もっと熱く高く 光よりも速く
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.55,0:16:36.07,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}Your Heart 連れてくよ HIGHER
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.48,0:16:53.45,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}圧倒的なStunning
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.45,0:16:55.10,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}感じてるはず Cuz, Why not? （是我吗？）
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.10,0:16:58.94,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}ドキドキをあげる C'mon, it's SHOWTIME!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:58.94,0:17:00.96,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}それっぽいは楽じゃねぇ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.96,0:17:03.09,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}物足りないでしょう So…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:09.38,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}Anyone can keep up with me, Anyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.38,0:17:13.42,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}「孤城」から見渡す景色
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:17.22,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}知ってるのは 私だけで
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.01,0:17:25.84,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}もっと Addictedに Intoxicatedに
Dialogue: 0,0:17:25.84,0:17:29.60,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}全部射抜いてあげろ Oh, I'm too GOOD!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.60,0:17:33.34,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}怖いものなんてない お遊びはもうおしまい
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.34,0:17:38.47,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}ここから全てが始まっていくよ
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.62,0:17:53.24,INYangMing,,0,0,0,,{\blur1\fad(150,150)}Cuz I'm the best of the BEST!
